{"tid":1479382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818 出唔出好？","createTime":"2019-08-17T01:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:36:14.000Z","uid":174907,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8309750398498e4e02bcaaf1be1f19e7f067326f","tid":1479382,"uid":174907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:26:51.000Z","msg":"［人手轉載］<br />\n<br />\n1. 仲猶疑緊818出唔出？你自問有呢兩樣嘢就應該出：良心 及 自我行動的能力<br />\n<br />\n2. 818衣著？民陣好似冇指定，但我覺得如果你怕比人認到，就著黑色，因為估計到時會係黑色居多，好多黑色佢就好難認。但今次遊行係想話比高牆上既人知社會上唔同階層既人都出來，而且個個都係香港既stakeholder，所以係鼓勵不同顏色。你想著乜色就乜色。<br />\n<br />\n3. 至於口罩最好就帶，原理同著咩色衫差唔多，你無顧慮就可以唔戴。<br />\n<br />\n4. 遮要帶，出街帶遮好正常。<br />\n<br />\n5. 得自己一個？其實好多人都係單機，但你出到來就會見到好多同伴，大家有同一個理念，係同一個地方，行同一條路。所以，絕對唔需要怕醜。但如果你想搵fd一齊討論下時事，歡迎你搵埋我。<br />\n<br />\n6. 民陣會係入口派發文宣品，poster之類既嘢，但亦都鼓勵大家自製文宣，自己發揮創意。當然你個人行出來已經好足夠。<br />\n<br />\n7. Popo淨係批左維園集會，但應該唔會有人理佢，每個人都係集完會想離開維園，但人數太多被逼出馬路行姐。所以我宜家呼籲警方開路。開路！開路！開路！<br />\n<br />\n8. 大家都知Popo基本上已經走火如魔，佢隨時可以彈出來射嘢，所以部份行得前小小既朋友都係要帶定基本裝備，頭盔眼罩口罩。記住，帶但似乎情況而戴，Be Water，絕對唔衝擊，唔set road block。<br />\n<br />\n9. 最後一點，唔需要太著緊捉鬼，鬼主要分兩種，一種係挑起事端，對於呢種絕對唔可以比佢煽動或者挑撥到，理性既朋友要幫手安撫情緒高漲既人。另一種鬼就係影相，拍片，佢目的係收集示威人士既樣貌，對於呢種，如果發現到就要盡量通知周圍既人警惕。<br />\n<br />\n10. 香港人加油！"},{"pid":"1b716b65c9b67918f5f42f684a95b2d989211ac8","tid":1479382,"uid":47337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"818<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7df39c37df8790a35faf7d1dd5e565b23e2693","tid":1479382,"uid":46578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"818 維園見"},{"pid":"d59c50a713b03781f470add06e2090e8d1d25590","tid":1479382,"uid":169207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"【 818 連 豬 Challenge 】連登仔快撚啲入黎畫連豬 Post Story!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpc75P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqpc75P6.jpg&h=799d28f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818連豬Challenge<br />\n畫連豬，post IG，tag三個朋友<br />\n比所有人都知818有民陣集會<br />\n每個人嘅宣傳都好緊要！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9689c5f4e51ade83e1a6706f0d8b9c9d887b760d","tid":1479382,"uid":174907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b716b65c9b67918f5f42f684a95b2d989211ac8","tid":1479382,"uid":47337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"818<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cc67b0ab560d5294146506fa5150f19f2ac86c","tid":1479382,"uid":174907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7df39c37df8790a35faf7d1dd5e565b23e2693","tid":1479382,"uid":46578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"818 維園見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a009f471469a12659b25d43ac0c11627670d9a","tid":1479382,"uid":174907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4208101bb4cc934d416351d6208e7a7ddc547736","tid":1479382,"uid":152519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:47:55.000Z","msg":"818 百萬大遊行!!!"},{"pid":"51239e23eb04277dc735d2221eeda345481fafe1","tid":1479382,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T